---
title: FridgeEnv — Episode Lifecycle
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Agent / LLM
    participant API as FastAPI Server
    participant Env as FridgeEnv
    participant Gen as Generator
    participant Scorer as Scorer

    Note over User,Scorer: 🔄 Episode Start

    User->>API: POST /reset {task_id: "hard", seed: 42}
    API->>Gen: generate_observation(seed=42, difficulty="hard")
    Note over Gen: Seeded RNG → deterministic<br/>30 items, 14-day horizon<br/>4-person household<br/>2 dietary restrictions<br/>Expiry clustering applied
    Gen-->>Env: Observation
    Env-->>API: Observation JSON
    API-->>User: {inventory, horizon, restrictions, ...}

    Note over User: 🤔 Agent Plans Meals
    Note over User: Day 1: shrimp + rice + broccoli<br/>Day 2: chicken + pasta + spinach<br/>...<br/>Day 14: tofu + quinoa + kale

    User->>API: POST /step {meal_plan: [...]}
    API->>Env: step(action)

    Note over Env: 📅 Day-by-day Simulation

    loop For each day 1..14
        Note over Env: Process meals for this day
        Env->>Env: Validate ingredients exist
        Env->>Env: Clamp to available quantity
        Env->>Env: Check dietary violations
        Env->>Env: Deduct from inventory
        Env->>Env: Track nutrition categories
        Env->>Env: Expire items past expiry date
    end

    Env->>Scorer: compute_reward(inventory, logs)
    Note over Scorer: 📊 Scoring<br/>Grader: used_perishables / total<br/>Waste: expired_items / total<br/>Nutrition: balanced_days / horizon<br/>Violations: -0.3 per breach

    Scorer-->>Env: Reward {score, waste_rate, nutrition_score, violations}
    Env-->>API: (observation, reward, done=true, info)
    API-->>User: {reward: {score: 0.73, ...}, done: true}

    Note over User,Scorer: ✅ Episode Complete — Score: 73%
